    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/ad1115a7727221ecc7eaf9cf2143b61f.poster.avif?t=1749033338\" width=616 height=285 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/ad1115a7727221ecc7eaf9cf2143b61f.webm?t=1749033338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/646b9ba06edce02f4ba28e30cc441caf.avif?t=1749033338\" width=616 height=72 /></span>柯蕾特是美丽的炼金术士普莉希拉的亲传弟子，她们在人迹罕至的深山当中过着无忧无虑的生活。柯蕾特日复一日地锻炼着自己的炼金技巧，希望自己有朝一日能成为像师傅一样，能够独当一面的炼金术士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是在某一天，普莉希拉在和一位奇怪的访客交谈许久之后，决定要踏上未知的旅途。尽管她没有向柯蕾特解释自己的目的，但她却把她在城市里的炼金工作室交给了柯蕾特。普莉希拉对柯蕾特说，“你要尽可能为需要你的人提供帮助。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突然当家做主的柯蕾特遵从了师傅的意愿，开始一边锻炼自己的炼金技巧一边帮助身边遇到了困难的人们。但她还不知道，她在今后的生活中不光会结识许多个性迥异的伙伴们，还会被卷入一场影响整个世界的命运的巨大阴谋当中……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/9e3c366195fb2fae19af6fdded5f09c1.poster.avif?t=1749033338\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/9e3c366195fb2fae19af6fdded5f09c1.webm?t=1749033338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>在冒险者公会接受各种委托，然后在炼金工作室当中制作各种能帮助她身边的人们的道具，让柯蕾特成为声名远扬的炼金术士吧！只要运用炼金术，您就可以制造药水、武器、防具……以及您能想象到的一切！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >稀有的炼金材料是不会随处可见的，您要去各种危险的地方收集这些材料。但当您认识了新的伙伴之后就可以雇佣伙伴和您组队，一起前往材料所在的地点。大森林，洞穴深处，甚至是残破的古城……只要有伙伴在身边，就没什么好怕的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了普通的道具和装备以外，柯蕾特还可以使用炼金术制作既美观又强大的服装。想让皇家勇者穿上忍者服？还是想让全国最强大的魔法师打扮成巫女？换不换装，换上什么装，这些全都由您说了算！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/46ed54ae0c182759e8905c8cbf0ca78b.avif?t=1749033338\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/f4d51849a845480203ad8986fc4c20d9.avif?t=1749033338\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/e4cbe4632fc505cc5aeb0c2e2e84109d.avif?t=1749033338\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/d49f6090bd0a8683ed370e89b80b08d6.avif?t=1749033338\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/e58966c01d861997f561895e5c88aef1.avif?t=1749033338\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135830/extras/81887a2d6f8baa79fcc25424b5ef5c58.avif?t=1749033338\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>性格各异的角色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内向的魔法师，无厘头的偶像，正在寻找真爱的兽人，青涩的勇者……有了这些伙伴陪在身边，您的冒险之旅一定会妙趣恒生！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>出类拔萃的RPG游戏体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种类繁多的招式和法术能让您的每一场战斗都充满紧张感和新鲜感！除此之外，您还可以将通过战斗获取的经验值自由分配给每一位冒险者，来打造您心目中的最强团队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在冒险者公会寻求委托！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险者公会接下委托吧！您可以通过完成委托来获取报酬和名声，但对柯蕾特来说，能够帮到其他人这件事本身就已经比报酬和名声有意义多啦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富多彩的炼金系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用炼金术来创造您所需要的一切吧！但可别以为物品制作出来之后就和炼金术没关系了……因为您还可以通过在冒险中获得的材料来进一步强化各种服装哦！</p>",
